# Sprint board maintenance

`SPRINT.md` is the live sprint view. Keep it accurate in the **same session** as story work.

## Before starting work

1. Read `SPRINT.md` — only implement **In scope**, **Stretch**, or **In progress** stories.
2. Story IDs are `W-01-Sxx` — verify against `BACKLOG.md`.
3. Do not start out-of-scope stories without explicit approval.

## When you begin a story

1. Move story to **## In progress**.
2. One story **In progress** at a time unless parallel work requested.
3. Leave checkbox unchecked until done.

## When a story is complete

Acceptance criteria pass; tests green where applicable.

1. Check box in **In scope** (or **Stretch**).
2. Remove from **In progress**; add line under **Done**.
3. Update `CHANGELOG.md` per `changelog.mdc`.
4. Log decisions in `DECISIONS.md` if qualified.

Mention in reply: "Sprint: W-01-Sxx → Done".

## Blockers

Add under **## Blockers / notes** — do not move to Done.

Do not ask permission to update sprint status on normal completion.
